PageContent.description:
Page content panel structure for badges and other complex page layouts.
This represents a panel that can contain various components like text, images, buttons, etc.

 {
  "type": "panel",
  "heading": "Welcome",
  "width": 12,
  "component": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": {"type": "doc", "content": [...]},
      "width": 12
    }
  ]
}

