TipTapContent.description:
TipTap Editor JSON content.

This DTO accepts any valid TipTap JSON structure, including complex content with:
- Text with marks (bold, italic, links, textStyle with inline CSS)
- Paragraphs with attrs (classes and inline styles)
- Lists, headings, code blocks, tables, etc.
- Nested content structures

The validation is intentionally minimal to accommodate the wide variety of
TipTap content that can be generated by the editor.

 {
  "type": "doc",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {"type": "text", "text": "Hello World"}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

 {
  "type": "doc",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "class": "custom-class",
        "style": "color: red; font-size: 16px;"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {"type": "bold"},
            {"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://example.com"}}
          ],
          "text": "Bold linked text"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

